headline: FirstEnergy Holds 2025 Annual Meeting
summary: In his address at the FirstEnergy Corp. (NYSE: FE) 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders today, Board Chair, President and Chief Executive Officer Brian X. Tierney said FirstEnergy has made significant progress toward its goal of becoming a premier electric company.
